{
  "analysis": "We attempted to build SQLite using a script, but no output was produced and the sqlite3 binary was not installed into /app/sqlite/bin. which sqlite3 returned nothing, and sqlite3 --version failed. This suggests the build did not occur or the script's logic failed to extract/compile. We need to inspect the /app/sqlite directories, confirm extraction of the tarball, verify gcc availability, and perform a manual build using the vendored tarball.",
